          "reviewBody": "The school has a holistic curriculum to cater to the developmental needs of the students. Through innovative projects and group/individual activities students learn from their peers. The recent G20 project was one such amazing experience which provided knowledge and exposure to students about various countries, their culture, customs, famous places, food etc. it was fun to watch students learn while they do such projects with full enthusiasm. Kudos to the teachers and management for keep doing such activities time to time.\nI am very happy and satisfied as a parent.",
